e intro paragraph describing `event_confirm` and its behavior needs to be included somewhere, and since there's no h2 heading above it, I'll treat it as its own section. Looking at the actual structure, I see three main sections marked with `===` underlines: コードサンプル, 仕様, and 内部構造・改修時の留意点. So I'll create four sections total—starting with an overview section for the intro content, then the three marked sections. I'm organizing this into sections that match the document structure: an overview section covering the intro content about event_confirm behavior, then the code samples, specifications table, and implementation notes sections. 続けて、stopとrevertの属性について説明しています。stopはダイアログキャンセル時にイベントの伝播とデフォルト動作を抑制するかどうかを制御し、デフォルトはtrueです。revertはキャンセル時に入力値を元の状態に戻すかどうかで、changeイベント時のみ有効です。そして内部実装の詳細として、このコンポーネントを構成するファイルパスを列挙しています。 I'm organizing the document structure with four main sections covering overview, code examples, specifications, and internal implementation details. Now I'm drafting the overview section to explain how the event_confirm action works—when users click cancel, it stops event propagation and reverts changes if it's a change event, while clicking OK allows the event to continue and execute its default action.\n\nI should note that since this uses the browser's native dialog component, its appearance and behavior depend entirely on the client environment and browser, so CSS styling and custom titles aren't possible. Then I'm moving into a code example showing how to display a confirmation dialog when selecting a specific dropdown item, followed by the specifications section that outlines all available attributes.\n\nNow I'm looking at the attribute specifications table, which shows whether each attribute is required, optional, or ineffective in server versus local contexts—things like the title for documentation purposes, the message text that appears in the dialog, and the condition selector that determines when the dialog displays. revertプロパティのデフォルト値は'true'で、changeイベント発生時にのみ意味を持つ。次に、このイベントアクションの実装に関わるファイルパスを確認すると、確認ダイアログの実体となるタグファイル、alert/confirmで共通の内容を実装するタグファイル、そしてダイアログ表示機能を担当するJavaScriptコンポーネントがある。 Since there's no base URL provided and no Javadoc references in the content, the official_doc_urls array will be empty. Now I'm ready to assemble the final JSON output.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":17940,"cache_read_input_tokens":18643,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":17940,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d0b7437f-691d-4c3f-ab11-6c57cb70d2f4","uuid":"061325fc-5b16-41df-a22c-8e321990a3c8"}
